        {
            "title": "全日收市︱午後再回 恒指跌140點報25752點 重磅科股領跌 新興科股逆市揚",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股午後反覆向下，尤幸未失守早市低位，「ATMXJ」等科磅科股幾乎全線報跌，新興的AI應用類科股則逆市再升，迅策(03317)便不斷破頂。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"迅策招股書封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"迅策招股書封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/03317.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">迅策招股書封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數今早低開136點，初段跌幅曾擴大至239點，見25653點即現反彈，早市中段最高曾見25852點，僅跌40點，其後進入在25750點之上反覆調整階段，午後一度升越早市高位，最高報25854點，跌38點，但後段跌幅再度擴大至過百點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指最後收報25752點，跌140點或0.54%。恒生科技指數明顯跑輸大市，收跌101點或2.06%，報4821點；國企指數跌65點或0.75%，報8611點。主板成交縮減至2449.77億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15852447-%e5%85%a8%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e5%9b%9e-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c140%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125752%e9%bb%9e-%e9%87%8d%e7%a3%85%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e8%b7%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK-5.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 16:18:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股收跌  滬股午後再下滑",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股收跌，滬股午後擴大，兩市成交合計21340.47億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證綜指全日收報3966，跌28點或0.72%，今早以3967點開市，跌27點或0.69%，上午見3979，跌16點或0.4%，為全日高位，午後進一步下挫，低見3955，跌40點或1%，為全日低位，全日成交9024.82億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指全日收報13996，跌46點或0.33%，今早開市報13928點，亦跌114點或0.81%，最低見13891，挫151點或1.08%，為全日低位，上午中段見14058，升16點或0.11%，為全日高位，午後窄幅，全日成交12315.65億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數全日跌29點或0.64%，報4566點 ; 創業板指數全日報3323，跌24點或0.73%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15852037-a%e8%82%a1%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c-%e6%bb%ac%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%86%8d%e4%b8%8b%e6%bb%91",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-9.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 15:08:41",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "迅銷中期純利升19.6% 中期息每股320日圓勝預期 上調全年盈利與股息預測",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">迅銷(06288)公布，截至今年2月底止半年純利按年升19.6%，擬派中期息每股320日圓；公司已上調全年盈利與股息預測。該股將於明早復牌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：迅銷官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230713-164619_source-web_6288_UNIQLO_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：迅銷官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/bplib_20230713-164619_source-web_6288_UNIQLO_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：迅銷官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司期內母公司擁有人應佔溢利2792.9億日圓，較去年同期的2335.66億日圓增長19.6%。每股中期息較去年同期提升33.3%，較原先預測的270日圓也高18.5%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">迅銷現時預測，本財年末期息每股將達320日圓，較原先預測的270日圓高18.5%；估計全年每股派息合共640日圓，按年提升28%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">除了上調全年派息預測外，迅銷亦將全年收益、經營溢利、母公司擁有人應佔溢利等預測全部調升，上調幅度介乎2.6%至7.7%。按新預測，公司估計全年純利達4800億日圓，較上財年增長10.9%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：迅銷官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240423_FI_source-web_06288-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：迅銷官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240423_FI_source-web_06288-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：迅銷官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">在截至今年2月底止半年，迅銷綜合收益逾2.05萬億日圓，按年升14.8%；反映事業本身利潤的事業溢利總額為3869億日圓，增長28.3%。整體錄得收益、溢利雙雙大幅增長，創歷來最佳業績水平。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">旗下UNIQLO(優衣庫)事業以開展旗艦店為主軸的品牌策略，除了冬季商品外，全年性商品銷售亦表現亮麗，隨著持續開展商品支柱多元化，UNIQLO事業於各個地區皆錄得收益及溢利雙增長。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">期內集團綜合毛利率為54.1%，按年提升0.8個百分點；銷售、一般及行政開支佔收益總額比率為35.3%，按年升1.2個百分點。稅前溢利總額達4288億日圓，按年增長17.9%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851891-%e8%bf%85%e9%8a%b7%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e7%b4%94%e5%88%a9%e5%8d%8719-6-%e4%b8%ad%e6%9c%9f%e6%81%af%e6%af%8f%e8%82%a1320%e6%97%a5%e5%9c%93%e5%8b%9d%e9%a0%90%e6%9c%9f-%e4%b8%8a%e8%aa%bf%e5%85%a8%e5%b9%b4",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-web_06288-6-4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 15:03:22",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
