            "title": "日股全日回吐413點或0.73%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股午後反覆再回，日經平均指數收市時跌幅擴大至413點或0.73%，收報55895點。</p>\n</div>",
