            "title": "台股反覆收升0.29%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股全日呈好淡爭持狀態，臨收市時抽高；台灣加權指數收報34861點，升99點或0.29%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15851705-%e5%8f%b0%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%8d%e8%a6%86%e6%94%b6%e5%8d%870-29",
